Note: pyproject.toml currently declares `license = { text = "MIT" }`,
which predates this file and is inconsistent with it. This inconsistency
was present in the project as handed off and is flagged here rather than
silently resolved one way or the other -- a maintainer should pick one
license deliberately before any real distribution.
